Reg Nullify in Concert is a track on the Hitch-Hiker's Guide to the Galaxy TV Theme Music vinyl released in 1980. It is a recording of the singer Reg Nullify and his band, the Cataclysmic Combo.Lyrics
Your arms, your legs, your heads

You're everything to me

I mean through all eternity.

Your glistening scales of green -

I don't know where they've been.

You might have laid a Treen,

But I don't care

You are my everything

You are everywhere. Radio LP 
